Submitted Files
---------------
README              
Main.jack - the Main class of the game
Board.jack  - represents a board in the 4-in-a-row game
Piece.java  - represents a piece in the game
Game.jack - class represents the game.



Remarks
-------
* We decided to implement a 4-in-a-row game. The game is a game of
  two players, the white and the black players. In order to choose 
  the column where to put the piece use the arrow keys(left and right).
  In order to release the piece in the column press the space key.
